{
  "stem": "3855.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my brother, the good-looking guy that he was, went up to the Joint Committee and gave them a nice story.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they gave us some francs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we stayed a whole week in Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we went to the Folies Bergere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And we really savored that freedom like I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was like-- From there, we went to the harbor-- my brother, my sister, and I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It wasn't that simple.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My father took us to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The three of us got on to the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We looked out the window.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this man ran with the train-- and waving goodbye until the end of the-- [CRYING] And that-- those things stay in your mind.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's not so easy to send three children away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "My mother stayed home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She couldn't handle it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And my father subsequently had a stroke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But he didn't die from it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He was taken to the camp anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were taken to Theresienstadt in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well there's a letter, a little postcard here from my mother from Theresienstadt and also letters from my mother, in which she says that my father is suffering badly, and that she tries to limit his pain, but that he's very sensitive, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he passed away in Theresienstadt, my father--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of normal causes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- I, I know that they lived in Vienna for several years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It must have been in '43.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to America.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We landed in New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A relative had sent somebody to pick us up, put us into a rooming house for one night on the west side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I marveled at the big sign of American Biscuit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't get over it, how big a company can be that makes biscuits.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
